<normalizedToken id="3B440EC5C00A4363C4D50D7B8F40ACF8" originalValue="“…" pageNumber="529">&quot;...</normalizedToken>
must be accepted as manifesting the type of the species botanically&quot;, he also referred (pl. 7) to the LINN specimen as 
<normalizedToken id="89F5E914D9175B9CE71BADF7B27F3EEA" originalValue="“type”" pageNumber="529">&quot;type&quot;</normalizedToken>
. Watt therefore failed to make an effective type choice.
